Itemized Passive Description:
*Basic effect(s)*
- Ki +3
- ATK & DEF 200%{passiveImg:up_g}
- Randomly changes Ki Spheres of a certain Type (PHY
excluded) to PHY Ki Spheres
- All allies' Ki +3 and ATK 50%{passiveImg:up_g} (self excluded)
- Receives an additional Ki +2 per PHY Ki Sphere obtained
- Receives an additional Ki +1 per Type Ki Sphere obtained
(PHY excluded)
*When receiving an attack*
- DEF 30%{passiveImg:up_g} for every 3 Ki
*When receiving a Super Attack*
- Damage reduction rate 30%{passiveImg:up_g} temporarily
*When attacking with 12 or more Ki*
- ATK 150%{passiveImg:up_g}
*When attacking with 18 or more Ki*
- Launches 2 additional attacks, each of which has a high
chance of becoming a Super Attack
*When attacking with 24 Ki*
- Attacks are effective against all Types
*When there is another "Movie Heroes" or "All-Out Struggle"
Category ally attacking in the same turn*
- Damage reduction rate 15%{passiveImg:up_g}
- All allies' DEF 77%{passiveImg:up_g} for 2 turns
